♫  Alone, I fight the disasters; the world is in a turmoil  ♫

15
00:01:08,080 --> 00:01:10,240
♫  Don’t scorn me for being ordinary  ♫

16
00:01:10,240 --> 00:01:13,440
♫  Keep a kind heart, be decisive and kill if need be  ♫

17
00:01:13,440 --> 00:01:15,660
♫  There are hidden joys and sorrows in fate  ♫

18
00:01:15,660 --> 00:01:18,000
♫  Between life and death, I strive to save a desperate situation  ♫

19
00:01:18,000 --> 00:01:20,080
♫  Faith carries me through the long and endless night  ♫

20
00:01:20,080 --> 00:01:23,415
♫  I will return with an enlightened heart  ♫

21
00:01:25,920 --> 00:01:29,960
♫  Extraordinary after final training, I enter the vast three realms 

22
00:01:29,960 --> 00:01:32,470
♫  And achieved nirvana in the cycle of reincarnation  ♫

23
00:01:32,470 --> 00:01:35,980
   

24
00:01:35,980 --> 00:01:38,892
   

25
00:01:43,420 --> 00:01:46,300
   

26
00:01:46,300 --> 00:01:48,490
 He's back. 

27
00:01:48,490 --> 00:01:50,550
 And he brought someone with him. 

28
00:02:09,690 --> 00:02:11,980
 Who's that person with the mask? 

29
00:02:13,860 --> 00:02:16,910
What's the progress of your chant?

30
00:02:17,470 --> 00:02:20,840
You're asking too early. It's not time yet.

31
00:02:23,320 --> 00:02:27,460
The world is so vast. No matter where I go,

32
00:02:27,460 --> 00:02:30,010
I always worry about you.

33
00:02:30,010 --> 00:02:33,130
 Physician Mo's face is looking more lifeless. 

34
00:02:39,390 --> 00:02:40,800
Show me your hand.

35
00:02:40,800 --> 00:02:45,370
 Since you lied to me first, I see no reason to tell you the truth. 

36
00:02:45,370 --> 00:02:50,260
 The power of Level Five can let me control the strength and weakness of my vital energy. 

37
00:02:50,260 --> 00:02:54,980
 If I control it at Level Three, he won't notice my progress. 

38
00:03:01,100 --> 00:03:04,950
I told you not to play tricks in front of me.

39
00:03:06,850 --> 00:03:08,950
How will you punish me?

40
00:03:09,690 --> 00:03:13,350
Not bad. I indeed chose the right person.

41
00:03:13,350 --> 00:03:15,740
You can remain calm now.

42
00:03:15,740 --> 00:03:18,310
But don't worry, you'll be fine.

43
00:03:18,310 --> 00:03:21,130
Your deadline for a year is not up yet.

44
00:03:21,130 --> 00:03:24,430
But it's already been so long.

45
00:03:24,430 --> 00:03:28,560
Why is your cultivation still stuck at Level Three?

46
00:03:29,489 --> 00:03:31,359
I did my best.

47
00:03:34,660 --> 00:03:40,080
Do you know what I previously let you consume?

48
00:03:41,350 --> 00:03:43,770
 Consume this. 

49
00:03:48,560 --> 00:03:51,650
That medicine is called the Corpse Worm Pill.

50
00:03:51,650 --> 00:03:54,420
Perhaps, it's not a medicine.

51
00:03:54,420 --> 00:03:58,960
It's a worm's egg concocted with a secret method.

52
00:03:58,960 --> 00:04:02,700
Once swallowed, it hides in your body.

53
00:04:02,700 --> 00:04:04,930
But don't worry.

54
00:04:04,930 --> 00:04:07,810
You'll be completely safe for now.

55
00:04:07,810 --> 00:04:12,080
As long as, within a year,

56
00:04:12,780 --> 00:04:16,260
you take my antidote regularly,

57
00:04:16,260 --> 00:04:21,300
that egg will dissolve on its own without leaving any side effects.

58
00:04:21,300 --> 00:04:23,680
Otherwise...

59
00:04:27,310 --> 00:04:32,740
it'll absorb nutrients inside your body, hatch,

60
00:04:32,740 --> 00:04:36,900
and start eating every last one of your organs,

61
00:04:36,900 --> 00:04:42,400
until you die slowly in unspeakable pain.

62
00:04:45,000 --> 00:04:50,380
Besides, a few days ago, I went to Qingniu Town.

63
00:04:50,980 --> 00:04:55,470
I saw your family from a distance. They're doing fine

64
00:04:55,470 --> 00:04:57,990
and eating big pancakes.

65
00:04:57,990 --> 00:05:02,570
As your younger sister, she's grown into a young lady.

66
00:05:02,570 --> 00:05:03,740
She's quite a beauty.

67
00:05:03,740 --> 00:05:05,610
I swear!

68
00:05:05,610 --> 00:05:09,020
In three months, I'll reach Level Four.

69
00:05:09,020 --> 00:05:13,260
This is more like it.

70
00:05:19,300 --> 00:05:20,420
All right then.

71
00:05:20,420 --> 00:05:22,420
I'll stay here in the valley for three months.

72
00:05:22,420 --> 00:05:24,590
I'm not going anywhere else.

73
00:05:27,762 --> 00:05:31,000
I went through a lot of effort to find these pills for you.

74
00:05:31,000 --> 00:05:33,970
It'll greatly help your cultivation.

75
00:05:36,140 --> 00:05:40,020
Do whatever you want during these three months.

76
00:05:40,020 --> 00:05:43,300
Rest assured, I won't keep watch on you again.

77
00:05:43,300 --> 00:05:49,800
But... if you still haven't achieved it by then,

78
00:05:51,030 --> 00:05:56,610
our lives will expire after these three months.

79
00:06:07,160 --> 00:06:09,620
 Only three months left. 

80
00:06:09,620 --> 00:06:11,750
 I must make the most of it. 

81
00:06:30,190 --> 00:06:33,380
That brat even learned to make poison!

82
00:06:33,380 --> 00:06:35,620
I didn't teach him this.

83
00:06:35,620 --> 00:06:40,260
This rotten brat is so ruthless

84
00:06:40,260 --> 00:06:43,270
and ungrateful to the core.

85
00:06:44,850 --> 00:06:46,580
 I've only just started cultivating. 

86
00:06:46,580 --> 00:06:51,000
 I can't rely on normal tactics to defeat someone like Physician Mo. 

87
00:06:51,000 --> 00:06:55,050
 Li Feiyu found a tactic for me. It's called the Secret Manual of the Blinking Sword Technique. 

88
00:06:55,050 --> 00:06:59,110
 He said it suits someone like me without any foundation. 

89
00:06:59,110 --> 00:07:03,810
 Instead of a sword technique, it's more like a technique for assassination. 

90
00:07:03,810 --> 00:07:07,800
 It's about using your surroundings, setting traps, 

91
00:07:07,800 --> 00:07:11,430
 manipulating lights and shadows to mislead your enemy, 

92
00:07:11,430 --> 00:07:14,980
 so you can land a fatal strike. 

93
00:08:04,340 --> 00:08:07,580
 

94
00:08:17,870 --> 00:08:20,700
 I've finally reached Level Six. 

95
00:08:20,700 --> 00:08:24,290
 All my five senses have grown sharper. 

96
00:08:24,290 --> 00:08:26,680
 From the gurgle of distant streams 

97
00:08:26,680 --> 00:08:30,185
 to the flutter of nearby insect's wings, 

98
00:08:30,185 --> 00:08:32,885
 I can sense them with perfect clarity. 

99
00:08:59,650 --> 00:09:02,170
I give up!

100
00:09:02,170 --> 00:09:05,800
Teaching a disciple is really exhausting work!

101
00:09:05,800 --> 00:09:08,770
How do you get faster by the day?

102
00:09:08,770 --> 00:09:11,080
You're just a good master.

103
00:09:16,310 --> 00:09:18,080
Take this.

104
00:09:20,175 --> 00:09:24,295
It matches your Blinking Sword Technique perfectly.

105
00:09:25,070 --> 00:09:26,600
Thank you.

106
00:09:31,500 --> 00:09:33,510
I'm heading back now.

107
00:09:35,140 --> 00:09:36,800
Han Li.

108
00:09:37,670 --> 00:09:41,440
I don't know what you've been through lately.

109
00:09:41,440 --> 00:09:45,952
But no matter what happens, don't face it alone.

110
00:09:45,952 --> 00:09:48,402
Send a message by pigeon if you must.

111
00:09:49,450 --> 00:09:51,280
Take care.

112
00:10:02,630 --> 00:10:05,380
 The three months' deadline is up. 

113
00:10:05,380 --> 00:10:09,204
 Physician Mo, I'm coming for you. 

114
00:10:21,340 --> 00:10:25,499
 I've prepared whatever I can for today. 

115
00:10:25,499 --> 00:10:27,829
 I won't be afraid again. 

116
00:10:48,500 --> 00:10:51,370
You're punctual.

117
00:10:52,220 --> 00:10:53,990
Where's the antidote?

118
00:10:55,410 --> 00:10:57,220
Have you reached Level Four?

119
00:10:57,220 --> 00:10:58,910
Where's the antidote?

120
00:11:06,050 --> 00:11:08,900
When people fight to survive,

121
00:11:08,900 --> 00:11:14,280
they will unleash their unimaginable abilities.

122
00:11:26,620 --> 00:11:28,430
Take this.

123
00:11:39,530 --> 00:11:41,700
I have one more question.

124
00:11:42,980 --> 00:11:45,290
Speak.

125
00:11:45,290 --> 00:11:47,160
Did Zhang Tie

126
00:11:48,340 --> 00:11:50,870
really go home?

127
00:11:54,040 --> 00:11:55,880
Of course.

128
00:11:58,650 --> 00:12:00,650
You're lying!

129
00:12:00,650 --> 00:12:02,170
I made a pact with him.

130
00:12:02,170 --> 00:12:05,820
If we didn't amount to anything, we'd never go home!

131
00:12:07,620 --> 00:12:09,570
See?

132
00:12:09,570 --> 00:12:13,140
You only believed half of what I told you.

133
00:12:13,140 --> 00:12:18,660
You acted cautious, but you're laughably naïve.

134
00:12:18,660 --> 00:12:22,340
You already knew the answer,

135
00:12:23,650 --> 00:12:26,130
why even ask?

136
00:12:32,450 --> 00:12:37,142
You wanted me to cultivate to Level Four to remove your poison and cure you.

137
00:12:38,620 --> 00:12:41,020
In fact, that was a lie.

138
00:12:45,450 --> 00:12:47,650
Whatever you want to know,

139
00:12:48,690 --> 00:12:51,180
I will tell you.

140
00:12:54,290 --> 00:12:56,490
It's chilly out here.

141
00:12:57,570 --> 00:13:01,280
Come, let's talk inside.

142
00:13:05,450 --> 00:13:07,080
Come.

143
00:13:49,500 --> 00:13:52,130
Heaven is on my side.

144
00:13:54,620 --> 00:13:57,850
You've really reached Level Four!

145
00:13:59,449 --> 00:14:01,556
I'm not going to die!

146
00:14:01,556 --> 00:14:04,740
I'm only 37 years old.

147
00:14:04,740 --> 00:14:08,700
I've barely started living!

148
00:14:10,690 --> 00:14:13,340
Strange, isn't it?

149
00:14:13,340 --> 00:14:16,050
I look so old at the age of 37.

150
00:14:16,050 --> 00:14:20,620
Anyone who sees me would think I'm almost 80 and on death's door.

151
00:14:20,620 --> 00:14:25,760
If not for the strange poison in my body that I've struggled to suppress it,

152
00:14:26,380 --> 00:14:30,030
why would I go through all this trouble?

153
00:14:32,740 --> 00:14:34,380
Come here.

154
00:14:34,380 --> 00:14:36,030
Han Li.

155
00:14:36,550 --> 00:14:41,600
Today marks the end of our master and disciple bond.

156
00:14:43,450 --> 00:14:46,340
Show me what you've got.

157
00:14:46,340 --> 00:14:49,570
Let me see what you've prepared.

158
00:15:49,290 --> 00:15:52,170
In less than three months,

159
00:15:56,140 --> 00:15:59,860
you've achieved a lot.

160
00:15:59,860 --> 00:16:03,840
You really keep surprising me

161
00:16:09,290 --> 00:16:16,410
but my reputation wasn't built on medical skills alone.

162
00:16:34,220 --> 00:16:37,180
Do you think you can defeat me?

163
00:17:03,650 --> 00:17:09,370
My ultimate technique, the Demon's Silver Palm, 
    

164
00:17:13,570 --> 00:17:17,530
returns to the martial art community today.

165
00:17:28,810 --> 00:17:32,340
Be good. Calm down, my dear disciple.

166
00:17:33,277 --> 00:17:36,507
It'll all be over soon.

167
00:17:58,650 --> 00:18:00,930
Rotten brat,

168
00:18:00,930 --> 00:18:04,900
you even have a hidden trick?

169
00:18:25,020 --> 00:18:26,690
You poisoned me.

170
00:18:26,690 --> 00:18:29,620
You've the guts.

171
00:18:57,860 --> 00:19:00,240
"Hide your skills with and intelligence in clumsiness."

172
00:19:01,110 --> 00:19:02,950
You taught me that.

173
00:19:19,300 --> 00:19:21,520
Armored Puppet!

174
00:19:38,780 --> 00:19:41,480
"Hide cleverness with clumsiness."

175
00:19:41,480 --> 00:19:44,080
That's what I taught you.

176
00:19:53,340 --> 00:19:55,240
Iron Slave.

177
00:20:45,380 --> 00:20:47,070
Stop struggling.

178
00:20:47,070 --> 00:20:49,140
I created this puppet.

179
00:20:49,140 --> 00:20:51,770
He only listens to me.

180
00:21:07,740 --> 00:21:11,160
Relax, Han Li.

181
00:21:11,160 --> 00:21:13,890
We were master and disciple, after all.

182
00:21:13,890 --> 00:21:16,160
I won't let you suffer too much.

183
00:21:16,160 --> 00:21:19,730
Did you also harm Zhang Tie?

184
00:21:23,730 --> 00:21:25,620
Take a guess.

185
00:21:25,620 --> 00:21:29,550
He regarded you as father, and you still harmed him?

186
00:21:29,550 --> 00:21:32,610
I had no choice, too.

187
00:21:33,720 --> 00:21:36,610
He didn't have a spiritual root.

188
00:21:37,250 --> 00:21:41,010
He couldn't practice the Eternal Spring Technique.

189
00:21:41,010 --> 00:21:46,220
He was useless to me.

190
00:21:48,594 --> 00:21:50,894
Mo Juren!

191
00:21:52,880 --> 00:21:54,060
Stop wasting time talking to him.

192
00:21:54,060 --> 00:21:55,510
Do it now!

193
00:21:55,510 --> 00:21:57,600
What's the rush?

194
00:21:59,085 --> 00:22:01,180
At this point,

195
00:22:01,180 --> 00:22:05,030
as long as your Seven Ghosts Devouring-soul Curse works

196
00:22:05,680 --> 00:22:07,380
he can't escape.

197
00:22:07,380 --> 00:22:09,450
Who are you talking to?

198
00:22:09,450 --> 00:22:11,470
Whose voice is that?

199
00:24:03,540 --> 00:24:05,820
Don't be afraid.

200
00:24:05,820 --> 00:24:08,920
Don't resist.

201
00:24:08,920 --> 00:24:15,290
Just enjoy this grand feast I've spent years preparing.

202
00:24:16,310 --> 00:24:20,430
I can hardly wait for the thrill of rebirth.

203
00:24:24,010 --> 00:24:29,370
The Soul-devouring Seven Ghosts!

204
00:24:50,900 --> 00:24:52,560
Who are you?

205
00:24:58,440 --> 00:25:00,330
Take a look.

206
00:25:01,030 --> 00:25:03,960
This is what I used to look like.

207
00:25:12,750 --> 00:25:14,200
Don't be afraid.

208
00:25:14,200 --> 00:25:16,880
It won't hurt that much.

209
00:25:16,880 --> 00:25:18,200
Relax.

210
00:25:18,200 --> 00:25:22,030
Everything will end in a while.

211
00:25:22,030 --> 00:25:23,480
Hurry, use the Immobilizing Talisman!

212
00:25:23,480 --> 00:25:26,080
Don't let him bite his tongue!

213
00:25:40,750 --> 00:25:42,680
Hurry up!

214
00:25:42,680 --> 00:25:47,720
Or everything that you've done will be in vain!

215
00:25:47,720 --> 00:25:53,350
Everything of yours will belong to us!

216
00:25:59,440 --> 00:26:02,880
   

217
00:26:21,680 --> 00:26:23,240
Give me your body.

218
00:26:23,240 --> 00:26:25,720
Give it all to your master.

219
00:26:25,720 --> 00:26:27,590
Give it to me.

220
00:26:27,590 --> 00:26:29,960
- Give it to me!
 - Give it to me!

221
00:26:29,960 --> 00:26:32,510
Mine... It's mine!

222
00:26:32,510 --> 00:26:35,350
Give up everything you have. Hand it over!

223
00:26:35,350 --> 00:26:36,510
Hand it over!

224
00:26:36,510 --> 00:26:39,850
Give it all to your master!

225
00:26:39,850 --> 00:26:41,750
Hand it over! Hand it over!

226
00:26:41,750 --> 00:26:45,880
Hand it over! You're mine!

227
00:26:45,880 --> 00:26:47,640
You belong to me! Give it to me!

228
00:26:47,640 --> 00:26:49,550
- Give it to me!
- Give it to me!

229
00:26:49,550 --> 00:26:51,550
Hand it over! Hand it over!

230
00:26:51,550 --> 00:26:52,830
- Give it to me!
- Give it to me!

231
00:26:52,830 --> 00:26:54,270
- Hand it over!
- No!

232
00:26:54,270 --> 00:26:55,680
This is my body!

233
00:26:55,680 --> 00:26:58,190
All of you, get out!

234
00:27:10,680 --> 00:27:12,380
How did he break free?

235
00:27:12,380 --> 00:27:16,000
Didn't you say I could possess him with your curse?

236
00:27:16,000 --> 00:27:20,790
The curse I gave you could only hold the power of Level Four.

237
00:27:20,790 --> 00:27:24,400
As for him, he has reached Level Four.

238
00:27:24,400 --> 00:27:28,620
So, you want us to struggle and wear each other down,

239
00:27:28,620 --> 00:27:30,750
so that you could swoop in and take over?

240
00:27:30,750 --> 00:27:33,180
What do you think?

241
00:27:34,030 --> 00:27:35,750
You cunning evil person.

242
00:27:35,750 --> 00:27:37,880
I won't let you take him.

243
00:27:37,880 --> 00:27:39,550
He's my disciple!

244
00:27:39,550 --> 00:27:41,550
Enough talking.

245
00:27:41,550 --> 00:27:44,500
Let's settle this with skill!

246
00:28:18,550 --> 00:28:19,860
Level Six?

247
00:28:19,860 --> 00:28:21,010
He tricked us.

248
00:28:21,010 --> 00:28:23,600
He has reached Level Six!

249
00:28:28,340 --> 00:28:34,670
Han Li, Han Li... Looks like...

250
00:28:35,410 --> 00:28:37,900
I've really underestimated you.

251
00:28:37,900 --> 00:28:40,099
"Use obscurity to do good deeds overtly."

252
00:28:40,099 --> 00:28:41,880
That's what you taught me too.

253
00:28:41,880 --> 00:28:45,290
You truly are my worthy disciple.

254
00:28:46,210 --> 00:28:48,330
Now that it has come to this,

255
00:28:49,640 --> 00:28:51,810
do you still have anything to say?

256
00:28:56,250 --> 00:28:58,280
I don't.

257
00:29:08,450 --> 00:29:10,670
I've nothing else to say.

258
00:29:13,500 --> 00:29:16,625
That man just now was Yu Zitong.

259
00:29:16,625 --> 00:29:20,386
Once you're out, don't believe a word he says.

260
00:29:20,386 --> 00:29:22,587
Kill him immediately.

261
00:29:22,587 --> 00:29:25,340
A primordial spirit fears poison the most.

262
00:29:25,340 --> 00:29:28,970
Use what you used on me.

263
00:29:28,970 --> 00:29:31,720
That's enough.

264
00:29:31,720 --> 00:29:35,420
Also, he fears the light.

265
00:29:44,970 --> 00:29:46,610
Goodbye,

266
00:29:47,590 --> 00:29:49,230
Master.

267
00:31:25,900 --> 00:31:27,860
What about you?

268
00:31:27,860 --> 00:31:30,030
Do you have anything else to say?

269
00:31:30,030 --> 00:31:31,620
My name is Yu Zitong.

270
00:31:31,620 --> 00:31:34,190
I'm from an aristocrat family of cultivators.

271
00:31:36,270 --> 00:31:41,250
A cultivator, and from an aristocrat family?

272
00:31:41,250 --> 00:31:43,160
I understand.

273
00:31:43,160 --> 00:31:48,350
If you help me to find another body so that I can start over again,

274
00:31:48,350 --> 00:31:51,930
in return, I'll recommend you to my aristocrat family.

275
00:31:51,930 --> 00:31:54,410
 Don't believe a word he says. 

276
00:31:54,410 --> 00:31:56,640
 Kill him immediately. 

277
00:31:56,640 --> 00:31:59,380
 A primordial spirit fears poison the most. 

278
00:31:59,380 --> 00:32:03,011
 Use what you used on me. 

279
00:32:04,010 --> 00:32:06,590
In the world of cultivation, everything becomes easier

280
00:32:06,590 --> 00:32:08,540
with a strong clan behind you.

281
00:32:08,540 --> 00:32:10,520
How about it?

282
00:32:12,000 --> 00:32:16,900
You said the same thing to Physician Mo, didn't you?

283
00:32:16,900 --> 00:32:21,800
That lowly mortal, is he fit to be mentioned in our discussion?

284
00:32:23,820 --> 00:32:25,485
That's right, too.

285
00:32:25,485 --> 00:32:28,515
But he entrusted me with something for you.

286
00:32:36,250 --> 00:32:38,010
Get lost!

287
00:32:52,210 --> 00:32:53,880
Come out.

288
00:32:54,830 --> 00:32:56,620
Come out!

289
00:33:10,970 --> 00:33:12,570
 Also, 

290
00:33:13,360 --> 00:33:15,600
 he fears the light. 

291
00:33:17,550 --> 00:33:18,860
Let me out!

292
00:33:18,860 --> 00:33:20,800
What are you doing?

293
00:33:27,240 --> 00:33:28,830
Let me out!

294
00:33:28,830 --> 00:33:31,390
Let me out now!

295
00:33:36,680 --> 00:33:39,445
Whatever happened between you and Physician Mo,

296
00:33:39,445 --> 00:33:41,960
I couldn't care less.

297
00:33:41,960 --> 00:33:44,780
I just want to stay alive.

298
00:33:44,780 --> 00:33:49,530
I don't harm others and I won't let others harm me!

299
00:34:18,030 --> 00:34:23,260
Without Physician Mo's command, he indeed can't move.

300
00:35:05,240 --> 00:35:09,210
 You should like this place. 

301
00:35:09,210 --> 00:35:11,580
 No one will bother you 

302
00:35:11,580 --> 00:35:16,010
 because no one knows you're no longer alive. 

303
00:35:17,510 --> 00:35:23,800
 Master, rest here in peace. 

304
00:35:38,350 --> 00:35:42,440
Old man, you won't even spare me after you're dead.

305
00:35:54,740 --> 00:35:58,597
 Disciple Han Li, if you're reading this letter, 

306
00:35:58,597 --> 00:36:02,800
 it means I've lost, and you've won. 

307
00:36:02,800 --> 00:36:04,680
 Congratulations. 

308
00:36:05,380 --> 00:36:08,300
 I was helpless and resorted to this out of desperation. 

309
00:36:08,300 --> 00:36:09,480
 It was fate. 

310
00:36:09,480 --> 00:36:10,670
 It was destiny. 

311
00:36:10,670 --> 00:36:12,480
 Now that I'm dead, 

312
00:36:12,480 --> 00:36:15,230
 there's no point talking about who's right or wrong. 

313
00:36:15,230 --> 00:36:17,740
 It'd just be laughable. 

314
00:36:17,740 --> 00:36:21,480
 As for the poison in you from the Demon's Silver Palm, 

315
00:36:21,480 --> 00:36:24,000
 I've left you some antidote. 

316
00:36:24,000 --> 00:36:26,990
 It'll keep it suppressed for a few months. 

317
00:36:28,400 --> 00:36:30,670
 But to fully cure it, 

318
00:36:30,670 --> 00:36:35,010
 you'll need my family heirloom, the Sunwarmed Jade. 

319
00:36:35,010 --> 00:36:39,960
 Han Li, I've never owed anyone an explanation. 

320
00:36:39,960 --> 00:36:42,915
 Fate decides victory or defeat. 

321
00:36:42,915 --> 00:36:47,450
 However, my wife and daughter have nothing to do with this. 

322
00:36:47,450 --> 00:36:51,620
 I trust you'll know what to do. 

323
00:36:53,570 --> 00:36:58,130
 You kept asking me the whereabouts of Zhang Tie. 

324
00:36:58,130 --> 00:37:02,930
 Sadly, in this world, there's no Zhang Tie left. 

325
00:37:02,930 --> 00:37:07,840
 I never meant to kill him but he uncovered my secret. 

326
00:37:07,840 --> 00:37:11,660
 Thus, I had no choice but to use his body to forge 

327
00:37:11,660 --> 00:37:14,510
 a soulless and mindless puppet. 

328
00:37:14,510 --> 00:37:17,360
 I named him Iron Slave. 

329
00:37:23,000 --> 00:37:26,090
 This person's mind was completely wiped out. 

330
00:37:26,090 --> 00:37:27,880
 It moves at the sound of a bell. 

331
00:37:27,880 --> 00:37:32,600
 Bind it with your blood, and it obeys your will. 

