00:42:20,320 --> 00:42:23,110
   

377
00:42:23,110 --> 00:42:25,490
Seven Mystics Sect have suppressed us for many years.

378
00:42:25,490 --> 00:42:28,520
I'm here today to settle the score!

379
00:42:30,480 --> 00:42:33,220
   

380
00:42:43,410 --> 00:42:44,740
Kill!

381
00:42:44,740 --> 00:42:46,810
Kill them all!

382
00:43:12,900 --> 00:43:15,570
Sect Leader Wang, do you want to fight till the end?

383
00:43:15,570 --> 00:43:17,530
Sect Leader Jia,

384
00:43:18,320 --> 00:43:21,700
I won't let you destroy the foundation of Seven Mystics Sect.

385
00:43:21,700 --> 00:43:26,180
If I trigger the mechanism, the mountain will collapse!

386
00:43:28,190 --> 00:43:33,660
If you don't want us to fight till the end, why not hear me out?

387
00:43:35,010 --> 00:43:36,880
Sect Leader Wang,

388
00:43:37,400 --> 00:43:39,220
what do you have in mind?

389
00:43:39,220 --> 00:43:41,480
Stop the mechanism, and we'll talk!

390
00:43:52,340 --> 00:43:54,360
Qu Hun, hurry!

391
00:44:04,490 --> 00:44:06,030
I'm coming.

392
00:44:06,030 --> 00:44:07,530
Move back.

393
00:44:15,780 --> 00:44:17,336
Han Li!

394
00:44:17,336 --> 00:44:18,900
My good buddy!

395
00:44:18,900 --> 00:44:20,580
I knew you will show up when the sect is in trouble.

396
00:44:20,580 --> 00:44:22,010
They have invaded.

397
00:44:22,010 --> 00:44:23,880
Let's go and protect the Sect Leader now!

398
00:44:23,880 --> 00:44:26,620
   

399
00:44:29,660 --> 00:44:32,060
I, Wang Juechu, the Sect Leader

400
00:44:32,060 --> 00:44:36,810
agree with Jia Tianlong to settle this by a blood duel.

401
00:44:36,810 --> 00:44:38,960
Ten men on each side

402
00:44:38,960 --> 00:44:41,110
will fight till death.

403
00:44:41,110 --> 00:44:42,550
Li Zhanling of the Seven Mystics Sect!

404
00:44:42,550 --> 00:44:44,790
Liu Chong of the Seven Mystics Sect!

405
00:44:46,070 --> 00:44:48,130
Count me in!

406
00:44:51,132 --> 00:44:53,570
Li Feiyu of Outer Blade Hall is here!

407
00:44:53,570 --> 00:44:55,900
Who has the guts to fight me till death?

408
00:44:55,900 --> 00:45:01,110
 I really didn't want to get involved but I can't just watch him walk into death. 

409
00:45:03,740 --> 00:45:08,491
I won't sign the blood pact but I'll fight along with you.

410
00:45:08,491 --> 00:45:10,902
You're a physician. Why would you fight?

411
00:45:10,902 --> 00:45:13,130
- Step back!
- All of you, step back!

412
00:45:13,130 --> 00:45:14,820
I'll handle this!

413
00:45:14,820 --> 00:45:16,880
Martial Uncle Lu is here! We'll definitely win!

414
00:45:16,880 --> 00:45:19,230
Martial Uncle Lu, kill them!

415
00:45:32,880 --> 00:45:35,090
 

416
00:45:35,090 --> 00:45:39,330
Jia Tianlong, are you making fun of me?

417
00:45:43,590 --> 00:45:47,490
Even a lion goes full force when it's fighting a rabbit.

418
00:45:47,490 --> 00:45:49,920
Forgive the offense!

419
00:45:57,880 --> 00:45:59,940
 A cultivator? 
 

420
00:46:05,110 --> 00:46:06,440
 His level is lower than mine. 

421
00:46:06,440 --> 00:46:09,110
We have the help of a cultivator.

422
00:46:09,110 --> 00:46:11,290
Didn't expect that, right?

423
00:46:27,070 --> 00:46:29,230
- Martial Uncle!
 - Excellent!

424
00:46:29,230 --> 00:46:30,840
Excellent!

425
00:46:30,840 --> 00:46:32,010
Demon!

426
00:46:32,010 --> 00:46:34,230
How dare you act so wildly!

427
00:46:39,630 --> 00:46:42,260
You ant! Are you seeking death?!

428
00:46:58,800 --> 00:47:00,990
Know your ability!

429
00:47:01,860 --> 00:47:04,480
All of you will die today!

430
00:47:15,050 --> 00:47:17,620
Why won't this precious thing obey me?

431
00:47:26,180 --> 00:47:28,570
A cultivator!

432
00:47:38,150 --> 00:47:39,890
Han Li...

433
00:47:40,660 --> 00:47:42,530
Leave it to me.

434
00:47:45,180 --> 00:47:47,250
Senior Brother Li.

435
00:47:59,190 --> 00:48:00,550
This thing is not bad.

436
00:48:00,550 --> 00:48:01,820
I'll keep it.

437
00:48:01,820 --> 00:48:02,900
You!

438
00:48:02,900 --> 00:48:05,110
Which family are you from?

439
00:48:07,050 --> 00:48:09,410
Which family do you belong to?

440
00:48:09,410 --> 00:48:11,290
I'm from the Ye family of Qinling,

441
00:48:11,290 --> 00:48:13,460
just passing through on my way to Tainan Valley.

442
00:48:13,460 --> 00:48:14,700
I didn't mean to be your enemy.

443
00:48:14,700 --> 00:48:17,860
Since you're here, I'll back off.

444
00:48:17,860 --> 00:48:19,740
What nonsense is this?

445
00:48:19,740 --> 00:48:21,820
The Ye family from Qinling?

446
00:48:22,620 --> 00:48:24,520
I've heard of them.

447
00:48:25,716 --> 00:48:28,140
So why did you interfere?

448
00:48:28,140 --> 00:48:30,610
I... I merely took up his offer.

449
00:48:30,610 --> 00:48:33,540
I made an exception. I didn't mean to offend you!

450
00:48:34,010 --> 00:48:35,410
An exception?

451
00:48:35,410 --> 00:48:39,610
As cultivators, we really shouldn't meddle in mortal's affairs.

452
00:48:39,610 --> 00:48:42,760
But... I also had no choice.

453
00:48:44,710 --> 00:48:49,980
Since you've admitted your mistake, take back your Flying Sword Talisman.

454
00:48:49,980 --> 00:48:51,610
I'll accept your kindness.

455
00:48:51,610 --> 00:48:54,110
And you might want to stay away from these mortal ants,

456
00:48:54,110 --> 00:48:56,550
or you'll be tainted by their bad luck.

457
00:49:05,110 --> 00:49:08,890
- Great!
 - Great!

458
00:49:23,410 --> 00:49:25,050
 What kind of treasure is this? 

459
00:49:25,050 --> 00:49:26,810
 Even the Fireball Technique can't burn it. 

460
00:49:26,810 --> 00:49:28,500
   

461
00:49:30,440 --> 00:49:32,120
- Great!
 - Great!

462
00:49:32,120 --> 00:49:35,780
Sect Leader Jia, where are you going?

463
00:49:36,590 --> 00:49:39,565
Immortal Master, let's talk this through.

464
00:49:39,565 --> 00:49:41,740
I don't have any feud with you.

465
00:49:41,740 --> 00:49:46,580
If you're willing to spare my life, I'll gladly reward you handsomely!

466
00:49:51,090 --> 00:49:53,400
You kill people like mustard seeds. 
 (Kills without taking their lives seriously) 

467
00:49:53,400 --> 00:49:55,750
Have you never thought this day would come?

468
00:49:57,180 --> 00:50:00,820
Never mind about the rest. However,

469
00:50:00,820 --> 00:50:03,510
I won't spare your life.

470
00:50:05,180 --> 00:50:07,640
Will you take your own life

471
00:50:07,640 --> 00:50:09,710
or shall I do it for you?

472
00:50:11,570 --> 00:50:13,030
Brothers of the Wild Wolves Gang!

473
00:50:13,030 --> 00:50:14,940
Kill!

474
00:50:17,620 --> 00:50:18,991
Kill him!

475
00:50:18,991 --> 00:50:21,812
- Charge!  
 - Kill him!

476
00:50:24,320 --> 00:50:27,030
I'm dead either way...

477
00:50:29,710 --> 00:50:31,540
Sect Leader!

478
00:50:45,320 --> 00:50:47,740
Immortal Master, you saved Seven Mystics Sect from danger today.

479
00:50:47,740 --> 00:50:49,700
I'm extremely grateful.

480
00:50:49,700 --> 00:50:52,830
I wonder how we can reward you.

481
00:50:55,920 --> 00:50:59,420
I'll give you the position of Deputy Sect Master and one thousand taels of silver.

482
00:50:59,420 --> 00:51:02,700
All the elders and disciples will obey your orders.

483
00:51:02,700 --> 00:51:08,060
But the sect can only be handed over to you upon my death.

484
00:51:08,060 --> 00:51:10,035
What do you think?

485
00:51:16,400 --> 00:51:20,800
Why don't you first dismiss those who are lying in ambush?

486
00:51:36,930 --> 00:51:40,590
They were probably instructed by Elder Zhang.

487
00:51:42,037 --> 00:51:46,410
Immortal Master, I didn't mean to disrespect you.

488
00:51:46,410 --> 00:51:49,410
As a sect leader, there are things I can't control.

489
00:51:49,410 --> 00:51:54,090
You'll understand when you establish your own sect one day.

490
00:51:55,820 --> 00:51:57,340
Don't worry, Sect Leader.

491
00:51:57,340 --> 00:52:00,380
I won't stay for long in Seven Mystics Sect.

492
00:52:00,380 --> 00:52:05,070
I'll leave here for a distant place and will never return.

493
00:52:05,070 --> 00:52:09,220
But before I leave, I would like to make a deal

494
00:52:09,220 --> 00:52:12,080
that benefits us.

495
00:52:12,080 --> 00:52:14,770
Of course. No problem.

496
00:52:18,274 --> 00:52:20,794
You haven't even heard my terms yet.

497
00:52:21,930 --> 00:52:23,740
Immortal Master, please speak.

498
00:52:25,388 --> 00:52:27,324
Take Li Feiyu as your final disciple.

499
00:52:27,324 --> 00:52:31,940
Also, appoint him as the head of Outer Blade Hall.

500
00:52:33,860 --> 00:52:35,230
Fine.

501
00:52:35,230 --> 00:52:36,850
Anything else?

502
00:52:37,820 --> 00:52:41,450
He likes Elder Zhang's third daughter, Zhang Xiu Er

503
00:52:41,450 --> 00:52:43,960
but Elder Zhang dislikes him because he's from a poor family.

504
00:52:43,960 --> 00:52:45,880
I'll talk to him. It's not a big deal.

505
00:52:45,880 --> 00:52:47,570
Anything else?

506
00:52:49,340 --> 00:52:50,780
I have a third uncle

507
00:52:50,780 --> 00:52:52,999
who's an outer disciple.

508
00:52:52,999 --> 00:52:55,960
He brought me to the Seven Mystics Sect.

509
00:52:55,960 --> 00:52:59,810
- If anything happens to him, I hope you'll take care of him. 
 - Of course.

510
00:52:59,810 --> 00:53:01,360
No problem at all.

511
00:53:04,140 --> 00:53:07,570
I won't leave without gratitude.

512
00:53:08,860 --> 00:53:11,970
This is a rare and precious Nourishing Essence Pill.

513
00:53:11,970 --> 00:53:13,110
Keep it.

514
00:53:13,110 --> 00:53:16,290
It will save your life at a critical moment.

515
00:53:20,440 --> 00:53:22,230
Whatever you've said,

516
00:53:22,230 --> 00:53:25,720
I accept them all.

517
00:53:25,720 --> 00:53:27,290
Farewell.

518
00:53:31,560 --> 00:53:35,160
 ♫ That day I first saw you ♫ 

519
00:53:35,160 --> 00:53:39,000
 ♫ We held close, hearts full of joy ♫ 

520
00:53:39,900 --> 00:53:44,080
 ♫ We made a promise to reunite ♫ 

521
00:53:44,080 --> 00:53:48,280
 ♫ And walked into the unknown ♫ 

522
00:53:48,280 --> 00:53:52,040
 ♫ But now that we've met again... ♫ 

523
00:53:53,760 --> 00:53:56,030
I've always been a loner.

524
00:53:56,030 --> 00:53:59,590
Never thought I'd find a true friend like you.

525
00:53:59,590 --> 00:54:01,010
I may not be good at much,

526
00:54:01,010 --> 00:54:04,230
but I've never feared a fight!

527
00:54:04,230 --> 00:54:06,640
Since we're brothers now,

528
00:54:07,190 --> 00:54:10,620
if anyone ever dares to mess with you,

529
00:54:11,450 --> 00:54:15,180
just give them my name, Li Fei Yu!

530
00:54:15,180 --> 00:54:18,780
